deck: Dark things are happening in Westwood, and a group of women are at the root of it.
description:
A coven of witches offer a human sacrifice to Baphomet for knowledge and power. Meanwhile, author Jack Kurtzberg loses his brother to a hit and run accident and decides to move back home where he and his brother grew up, in hopes of breaking through his writer's block.

The neighborhood welcoming committee includes some of the coven members, and Jack's own past seems to have some dark overtones.

Collected in The Westwood Witches.
name: The Westwood Witches
